        {
          "type": "note",
          "id": "ALpsa",
          "name": "Sections 1-2 Implementation Spec",
          "width": 720,
          "height": 3200,
          "content": "# APEX MOTUS — Sections 1 & 2 Implementation Spec\n---\n\n## SECTION 1 — HERO (ChatGPT-Style Conversational Landing)\n\n### 1.1 Overall Structure\n\nThe Hero section is a full-width frame (width: 100vw, height: 900px) with absolute positioning (layout: none) for all children. It contains three layers stacked via z-order:\n\n1. Background — Photo fill with dark overlay\n2. Navigation bar — Top-aligned, full-width\n3. Center content block — Heading + subtitle\n4. Input area — Chat bar + suggestion chips\n\n### 1.2 Background Treatment\n\nThe hero frame uses a dual fill stack:\n\n  /* Base layer: dark navy solid */\n  background-color: #0a1028;\n\n  /* Top layer: Unsplash photo, fill mode, 35% opacity */\n  .hero::before {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    inset: 0;\n    background-image: url('/images/hero-bg.jpg');\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: center;\n    opacity: 0.35;\n    z-index: 0;\n  }\n\n- Photo: Unsplash image by Vladimir Ivanenko, object-fit: cover\n- Overlay opacity: 0.35 — lets the photo texture through while maintaining text legibility\n- Base color: #0a1028 (deep navy-ink) — NOT pure black\n\n### 1.3 Navigation Bar\n\nPositioned at top of hero frame, full width.\n\n- Layout: display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center\n- Padding: 32px 60px (vertical / horizontal)\n- Width: 1440px (full container)\n- Height: 84px (auto from padding + content)\n\n#### Logo\n- Content: APEX MOTUS\n- Font: Funnel Sans, 600 weight\n- Size: 16px\n- Letter-spacing: 4px\n- Color: #d4af37 (gold accent)\n\n  .nav-logo {\n    font-family: 'Funnel Sans', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n    color: #d4af37;\n  }\n\n#### Nav Links\n- Layout: display: flex; gap: 40px\n- Items: About, Features, Contact\n- Font: Funnel Sans, 400 weight, 14px\n- Letter-spacing: 2px\n- Color: #FFFFFFCC (white at 80% opacity)\n\n  .nav-link {\n    font-family: 'Funnel Sans', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n    text-decoration: none;\n  }\n  .nav-link:hover { color: #FFFFFF; }\n\n### 1.4 Center Content Block\n\nAbsolutely positioned within the hero.\n\n- Position: x: 320, y: 260 (centered in 1440px frame)\n- Width: 800px\n- Layout: flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 24px\n\n#### Main Heading\n- Content: Talk to Your (newline) AI Partner\n- Font: Playfair Display, 700 weight\n- Size: 72px\n- Line-height: 1.05 (tight)\n- Color: #FFFFFF (pure white)\n- Text-align: center\n- Width: 800px (textGrowth: fixed-width)\n\n  .hero-heading {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-size: 72px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 1.05;\n    color: #FFFFFF;\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 800px;\n  }\n\n#### Subtitle\n- Content: Unlock smarter decisions with a conversational AI built for enterprise consulting.\n- Font: Newsreader, 400 weight, 20px\n- Line-height: 1.5\n- Color: #FFFFFFBB (white at ~73% opacity)\n- Text-align: center, Width: 600px\n\n  .hero-subtitle {\n    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.73);\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 600px;\n  }\n\n### 1.5 Chat Input Bar\n\nPositioned absolutely below the center block.\n\n- Position: x: 410, y: 590\n- Width: 620px\n- Layout: flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 20px\n\n#### Input Field\n- Shape: Pill — border-radius: 999px\n- Background: #F4F2EF (warm off-white)\n- Height: 56px, Width: 620px\n- Padding: 0 28px\n- Layout: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center\n\n  .chat-input {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    width: 620px;\n    height: 56px;\n    padding: 0 28px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    background: #F4F2EF;\n    border: none;\n  }\n\n#### Placeholder Text\n- Content: Ask me anything…\n- Font: Newsreader, 400 weight, 16px\n- Color: #4A4A4A\n\n#### Send Button (inside input)\n- Shape: Circle, 36px x 36px, border-radius: 999px\n- Background: #0a1028 (same deep navy as hero base)\n- Icon: White arrow path, 14px x 14px, fill: #FFFFFF\n\n  .send-btn {\n    width: 36px; height: 36px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #0a1028;\n    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .send-btn svg { width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: #FFFFFF; }\n\n### 1.6 Suggestion Chips\n\n- Layout: display: flex; gap: 12px\n- Items: Analyze my data, Draft a proposal, Summarize insights\n\n#### Individual Chip\n- Shape: Pill — border-radius: 999px\n- Background: #FFFFFF1A (white at 10% opacity)\n- Border: 1px solid #FFFFFF22 (white at 13%)\n- Padding: 10px 20px\n- Font: Funnel Sans, 400 weight, 13px\n- Letter-spacing: 1px\n- Color: #FFFFFFCC (white at 80%)\n\n  .chip {\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.13);\n    font-family: 'Funnel Sans', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n  }\n  .chip:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18); }\n\n### 1.7 Color Palette Summary (Section 1)\n\n- Hero base: #0a1028 — Background solid fill, send button\n- Gold accent: #d4af37 — Logo text\n- White 100%: #FFFFFF — Heading, send icon\n- White 80%: #FFFFFFCC — Nav links, chip text\n- White 73%: #FFFFFFBB — Subtitle\n- White 13%: #FFFFFF22 — Chip border\n- White 10%: #FFFFFF1A — Chip background\n- Off-white: #F4F2EF — Input bar background\n- Dark grey: #4A4A4A — Placeholder text\n\n### 1.8 Animation Spec — Hero to Sticky Nav Transition\n\nOn scroll, the hero section transforms into a compact sticky navigation bar.\n\nTrigger: scroll > hero.offsetHeight - navHeight\nDelay: 100ms after threshold is reached\nDuration: 400ms, ease-out timing\n\n  // Pseudocode: Hero to sticky nav scroll handler\n  const hero = document.querySelector('.hero-section');\n  const nav = document.querySelector('.nav');\n  const DELAY = 100;\n  const DURATION = 400;\n  let timeout = null;\n\n  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {\n    const scrollY = window.scrollY;\n    const threshold = hero.offsetHeight - nav.offsetHeight;\n    if (scrollY >= threshold) {\n      if (!timeout) {\n        timeout = setTimeout(() => {\n          nav.classList.add('sticky');\n        }, DELAY);\n      }\n    } else {\n      clearTimeout(timeout);\n      timeout = null;\n      nav.classList.remove('sticky');\n    }\n  });\n\n  .nav {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;\n    transition: all 400ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .nav.sticky {\n    position: fixed; top: 0;\n    background: #0a1028;\n    padding: 16px 60px; /* compressed from 32px */\n    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n  }\n\nBehavior:\n1. User scrolls past hero bottom edge\n2. After 100ms delay, nav detaches and becomes position: fixed\n3. Nav compresses padding from 32px to 16px vertically\n4. Background gains backdrop-filter: blur(12px) + shadow\n5. Hero content slides up and out of view\n6. Scrolling back up reverses the transition\n\n---\n\n## SECTION 2 — ABOUT (What We Do)\n\n### 2.1 Overall Structure\n\n- Width: fill_container (matches parent = 1440px)\n- Height: 1100px\n- Background: #F4F2EF (warm light grey — maps to CSS var --background in light mode)\n- Layout: none (all children absolutely positioned)\n\n### 2.2 Monumental Bleeding Heading\n\nThe signature design element — a massive heading that intentionally overflows its container.\n\n- Content: WHAT WE DO\n- Font: Playfair Display, 700 weight\n- Size: 180px\n- Line-height: 1.0\n- Letter-spacing: -2px (tight tracking)\n- Color: #1A1A1A (near-black — maps to --card dark mode)\n- Text-align: center\n- Width: 1600px (exceeds 1440px container by 160px)\n- Position: x: -80, y: 120\n- textGrowth: fixed-width\n\nHow the bleed works: The text frame is 1600px wide, positioned at x: -80 within a 1440px parent. This creates a symmetrical 80px overhang on each side. The parent frame does NOT clip overflow, so the text visually bleeds beyond the section edges.\n\n  .about-heading {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-size: 180px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 1;\n    letter-spacing: -2px;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    text-align: center;\n    width: 1600px;\n    position: absolute;\n    left: -80px;\n    top: 120px;\n  }\n\n  /* Alternative: use negative margins */\n  .about-heading-alt {\n    width: 100vw;\n    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  /* IMPORTANT: parent must NOT have overflow: hidden */\n  .about-section { overflow: visible; }\n\nNote: snapshot_layout flags this as 'partially clipped' because the text exceeds parent bounds. This is INTENTIONAL.\n\n### 2.3 Gold Accent Divider\n\n- Shape: Rectangle\n- Width: 80px, Height: 3px\n- Color: #d4af37 (gold — same as logo)\n- Position: x: 680, y: 340 (centered in 1440px)\n\n  .gold-divider {\n    width: 80px; height: 3px;\n    background: #d4af37;\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 680px; top: 340px;\n  }\n\n### 2.4 Three-Column Editorial Grid\n\nPositioned below the heading and divider. Uses flexbox.\n\n- Position: x: 80, y: 440\n- Width: 1280px (1440 - 160px margin)\n- Layout: display: flex; gap: 60px\n\n#### Column 1 — Label (Left)\n- Width: 200px (fixed)\n- Content: OUR MISSION\n- Font: Funnel Sans, 400 weight, 12px\n- Letter-spacing: 3px\n- Color: #4A4A4A\n\n  .col-label {\n    font-family: 'Funnel Sans', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    color: #4A4A4A;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n\n#### Column 2 — Body (Center)\n- Width: fill_container (flex: 1 — takes remaining space, approx 760px)\n- Content: Full mission statement paragraph\n- Font: Newsreader, 400 weight, 18px\n- Line-height: 1.7 (generous reading rhythm)\n- Color: #1A1A1A\n- textGrowth: fixed-width (wraps within available width)\n\n  .col-body {\n    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    color: #1A1A1A;\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n\n#### Column 3 — CTA (Right)\n- Width: 200px (fixed)\n- Layout: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 8px\n- Text: Learn more + arrow (→)\n- Font: Funnel Sans, 400 weight, 13px / 16px for arrow\n- Letter-spacing: 2px\n- Color: #4A4A4A\n\n  .col-cta {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: flex-end;\n    gap: 8px;\n    width: 200px;\n    font-family: 'Funnel Sans', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    color: #4A4A4A;\n  }\n  .col-cta:hover { color: #d4af37; }\n\n### 2.5 Inset Photo\n\n- Position: x: 160, y: 680\n- Width: 420px, Height: 300px\n- Fill: Image fill, mode: fill (object-fit: cover)\n- Photo: Unsplash — Maxime Kirschner (architectural/abstract detail)\n\n  .about-photo {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 160px; top: 680px;\n    width: 420px; height: 300px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  }\n\nPlacement rationale: The photo sits at the left-third intersection, creating an asymmetric composition. The large whitespace on the right (~860px empty) balances the visual weight of the 180px heading above and gives the section room to breathe.\n\n### 2.6 Whitespace Rationale\n\n- Top margin (y: 120 for heading): 120px breathing room from section top\n- Heading to divider: ~220px gap (340 - 120 = heading height region)\n- Divider to grid: 100px gap (440 - 340)\n- Grid to photo: 240px gap (680 - 440)\n- Right emptiness: ~860px of open space right of the photo — intentional editorial white space\n- Bottom margin: 120px (1100 - 680 - 300 = 120px below photo)\n\nThis generous spacing follows editorial/magazine layout principles where whitespace is a deliberate design element, not wasted space.\n\n### 2.7 Gold Accent Usage Across Both Sections\n\nGold (#d4af37) appears as a consistent brand thread:\n1. Section 1: Logo text\n2. Section 2: Divider line\n3. Later sections: Likely CTA hover states, accent borders\n\nThis color does NOT map to any CSS variable in the design system — store as:\n  :root { --brand-gold: #d4af37; }\n\n### 2.8 Color Palette Summary (Section 2)\n\n- Background: #F4F2EF — CSS var --background (light) — Section fill\n- Near-black: #1A1A1A — CSS var --card (dark mode) — Heading, body text\n- Medium grey: #4A4A4A — Labels, CTA, placeholder\n- Gold: #d4af37 — Use --brand-gold — Divider accent\n\n---\n\n## FONT STACK SUMMARY\n\n- Playfair Display (700): Display headings — Hero H1, About bleeding heading\n- Newsreader (400): Body copy, subtitle, placeholder, input\n- Funnel Sans (400, 600): UI elements — nav, logo, labels, chips, CTAs\n\nGoogle Fonts load:\n  <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Newsreader:wght@400&family=Funnel+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap' rel='stylesheet'>\n\n---\n\n## IMPLEMENTATION STEPS\n\n### Section 1 — Hero\n1. Create <section> with position: relative; height: 100vh; min-height: 900px; overflow: hidden\n2. Add background image as ::before pseudo-element with opacity: 0.35 over #0a1028 base\n3. Build nav bar with flex layout, logo left, links right, padding: 32px 60px\n4. Center content block: absolutely position at top: 29%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%)\n5. Add heading with Playfair Display 72px/1.05, subtitle with Newsreader 20px/1.5\n6. Build chat input bar: pill shape (border-radius: 999px), #F4F2EF background, 56px height\n7. Place send button inside input: 36px circle, #0a1028, white arrow SVG\n8. Add 3 suggestion chips below input with gap: 12px, glass-morphism style\n9. Implement scroll observer for sticky nav transition (100ms delay, 400ms ease-out)\n10. Add backdrop-filter: blur(12px) and box-shadow to sticky state\n\n### Section 2 — About\n1. Create <section> with position: relative; height: 1100px; background: #F4F2EF; overflow: visible\n2. Add bleeding heading: width: calc(100% + 160px); margin-left: -80px; font-size: 180px\n3. Place gold divider: 80px x 3px, centered horizontally, below heading\n4. Build 3-column grid with flexbox: gap: 60px; padding: 0 80px\n5. Left column (200px fixed): uppercase label OUR MISSION\n6. Center column (flex: 1): body paragraph in Newsreader 18px/1.7\n7. Right column (200px fixed): Learn more → CTA, right-aligned\n8. Place inset photo at left: 160px; top: 680px; width: 420px; height: 300px\n9. Ensure parent has overflow: visible for the bleeding heading effect\n10. Add hover state on CTA: transition color to #d4af37"
